entity.name: Updates on the Covid-19 situation in the Philippines
entity.description: This page provides real-time updates on the Covid-19 situation from trusted and official sources.

text: The Philippines is “winning” in the fight against COVID-19, Malacañang said on Monday as it disputed the report of the WHO that the Philippines had the fastest rise in new coronavirus cases in the Western Pacific region. | @LeilasINQ https://t.co/R6ddvrycC5
